                            <comment id="15699575" author="fpin" created="Sun, 27 Nov 2016 11:57:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have the same issue between DateType and StringType on Sparkv 2.0.2, do you know if this pull request fixes it?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;in Spark 2.0.2 :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;spark-sql&amp;gt; select greatest(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2015-02-02&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, date(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2015-01-01&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)) ;
Error in query: cannot resolve &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;greatest(&apos;&lt;/span&gt;2015-02-02&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;, CAST(&apos;&lt;/span&gt;2015-01-01&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos; AS DATE))&apos;&lt;/span&gt; due to data type mismatch: The expressions should all have the same type, got GREATEST(string, date).; line 1 pos 7
&lt;/pre&gt;
